snippet.title: My Empire Gameplay (Playfish, 2011)
snippet.description:
Gameplay from the Facebook game My Empire I captured on 29 September 2011, a day before the game was taken offline. 

The game was developed in 2010 at the Playfish studio in Beijing. 

Sound wasn't captured unfortunately. Music on the video is by Random Mind: https://opengameart.org/content/medieval-the-bards-tale

Game and assets © Playfish/EA
